ck1\"></div>\n    <div class=\"top-image column1\">\n        \n    </div>\n    <!--网页主体部分 begin-->\n    <div class=\"page-main-box\">\n        <div class=\"page-main\">\n            <div class=\"left-menu\">\n                <div class=\"head\">\n\n\n\n师资队伍</div>\n                <div class=\"head-line\"></div>\n                <ul>\n      <a href=\"../../szdw/jsdw.htm\" title=\"教师队伍\"><li class=\"on\">教师队伍</li></a>\n    <a href=\"../../szdw/bssds1.htm\" title=\"博士生导师\"><li>博士生导师</li></a>\n    <a href=\"../../szdw/czxgzdjs.htm\" title=\"曾在系工作的教师\"><li>曾在系工作的教师</li></a>\n</ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"right-main-box\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;height:52px;\"></div>\n                <div class=\"right-main\">\n                    <div class=\"right-map\">\n                        \n\n\n\n<div class=\"left\">\n正高级\n</div>\n\n\n                        <div class=\"right\">\n    当前位置：\n                        <a href=\"../../index.htm\" style=\"color:#000;\">首页</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jsdw.htm\" style=\"color:#000;\">师资队伍</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jsdw.htm\" style=\"color:#000;\">教师队伍</a>\n</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <!--这里放主体显示部分-->\n                    <div class=\"szdw-detail right-column-box\">\n                        \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/photoswipe.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/klass.min.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n         <div id=\"vsb_content desc\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<div class=\"basic-box\">\n            \n <div class=\"timg\">\n  <img src=\"/__local/7/C4/F0/A2A7A5DDE909A7A9DABA53CD833_8560877F_7EE2.jpg?e=.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/7C4F0A2A7A5DDE909A7A9DABA53CD833/8560877F/7EE2?e=.jpg\" vheight=\"\" vwidth=\"\" orisrc=\"/__local/7/C4/F0/A2A7A5DDE909A7A9DABA53CD833_8560877F_7EE2.jpg?e=.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"> \n </div>\n <div class=\"tbasic\">\n               \n  <div class=\"tname\">\n   王  义\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"tposition\">\n   教授\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n  <div class=\"tcontent\">\n                  \n   <p>博士、教授</p>\n   <p>电话：010-62771960</p>\n   <p>邮箱：yiwang@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"right-column-menu tright-column-menu list-paddingleft-2\">\n \n <li class=\"on\"><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   教育背景\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   工作经历\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   教学工作\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   研究领域\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   研究概况\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   学术成果\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   学术兼职\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   奖励与荣誉\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<div class=\"tli-content jy-background tli-content-on\">\n <p>● 1996.9-1999.7 博士，清华大学工程物理系</p>\n <p>● 1991.9-1994.7 硕士，西北核技术研究所</p>\n <p>● 1986.9-1991.7 本科, 清华大学工程物理系</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content job-record tli-content-\">\n <p>● 2014.12-至今 &nbsp; 清华大学工程物理系 &nbsp; &nbsp; 研究员</p>\n <p>● 2006.6-2014.12 &nbsp;清华大学工程物理系 &nbsp; &nbsp; 副研究员</p>\n <p>● 2004.4-2006.5 &nbsp;清华大学物理系 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 博士后</p>\n <p>● 1991.7-2004.3 &nbsp;西北核技术研究所</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content jx-work tli-content-\">\n <p>● 讲授课程：</p>\n <p>　　1） 光电成像探测器原理及应用</p>\n <p>　　2） 电离辐射探测学</p>\n <p>　　3） 核仪器概论</p>\n <p><br></p>\n <p>● 研究生培养：</p>\n <p>　　毕业博士3人，其中1名在美国阿贡实验室做博士后研究。毕业硕士6人，其中2名</p>\n <p>　　在国外著名大学攻读博士学位。</p>\n <p>　　在读博士2名，硕士4名</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content yj-part tli-content-\">\n <p>● 辐射成像技术，偏重于高能快速辐射成像技术；</p>\n <p>● 高能物理探测器研究，各种新型气体探测器，如阻性板室，多气隙阻性板室，高计数率MRPC，飞行时间探测器等。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content yj-basic tli-content-\">\n <p>学术研究主要在两个方面，高能物理探测器和数字辐射成像技术。</p>\n <p>（一）高能物理探测器研究方面，紧密结合重大科学前沿课题、尤其是相对论重离子碰撞实验中对粒子精确鉴别的需求，开展了新型气体探测器－多气隙电阻板室（MRPC）的研究。在新型低电阻电极材料研发，高计数率探测器研发，工作机理研究，性能模拟及测试，制作工艺和质量控制等方面均取得了重大突破。</p>\n <p>　　1、研制出STAR－TOF的MRPC模块室，时间分辨优于70ps。实现了MRPC的批量制作，生产出三千多个MRPC探测器，产品合格率优于95％。整个TOF的时间分辨达到80ps，性能优良，运行稳定。STAR增加TOF后，大大提高了高动量区的粒子鉴别能力，极大扩展了STAR的物理性能，使一些原来很难开展但有重要意义的物理课题能够开展起来。</p>\n <p>　　2、中美核物理合作的重大项目“STAR 新型μ子探测器建造及相关物理研究”。研制出STAR实验的缪子探测器LMRPC。其时间分辨达70ps，位置分辨优于1cm，是国际上具有最宽读出条的MRPC。STAR缪子探测器能够很好的识别重味夸克粒子，对了解重离子对撞产生的物质状态的性质能提供许多信息，是研究QGP的良好探针，是STAR实验今后几年运行的主要探测器，将发挥重大作用。</p>\n <p>　　3、针对下一代高亮度下的高能物理实验的需求，在国际上独家研制出体电阻达1010Ωcm的低电阻玻璃。同时研制出了计数率高达70kHz/cm2的高计数率MRPC探测器，时间分辨优于40ps，综合性能达到国际领先水平。高计数率MRPC的研制成功解决了高亮度高能物理实验粒子鉴别的世界性难题。CBM实验已决定采用我们的技术建造TOF。</p>\n <p>（二）在辐射成像技术研究方面，进行了基于面阵探测器的数字X射线成像技术研究，在国内首次研制出便携式闪光X射线检查仪，性能指标达到国际同类产品先进水平，在公安、武警、海关和边防等部门得到广泛应用，取得了良好的经济效益和社会效益。研制出采用15MeV电子直线加速器的高能X射线火箭发动机实时检测系统，研制成功国内首套航空发动机高能X射线检测系统样机，稳态成像检测灵敏度大大优于ASTM 1－2T，瞬态成像检测灵敏度优于ASTM 2－2T，性能指标达到国际先进水平。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content xs-result tli-content-\">\n <p>发表论文一百多篇篇，其中SCI 收录53篇， 获得国家专利19项，</p>\n <p>代表性论文列表：</p>\n <p>　　1）STAR合作组. Observation of the antimatter helium-4 nucleus. Nature Vol 473, (2011)353-356</p>\n <p>　　2) Wang Yi, Wang Jingbo, et al. Production and quality control of STAR-TOF MRPC，Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics research A,2010, 613: 200-206</p>\n <p>　　3) Wang Jingbo, Wang Yi, et al. Development of multi-gap resistive plate chambers with low-resistivesilicate glass electrodes for operation at high particle fluxes and largetransported charges,Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics research A, 2010, 621:151-156</p>\n <p>　　4) Wang Yi, Chen Huangshan, et al. Performance of a new LMRPC prototype for the STAR MTD system，Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics research A,2011, 640: 65-69</p>\n <p>　　5)Wang Jingbo, Wang Yi, et al. Development of high-rate MRPCs for high resolution Time-of-Flight systems，Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics research A,2013, 713: 40-51</p>\n <p>　　6) Chen Huangshan, Wang Yi, et al. Production of Long-strip Multi-gap Resistive Plate Chamber module for the STAR-MTD system, JINST, 2012 7 P10006</p>\n <p>　　7)Zhu Weiping, Wang Yi. et al. &nbsp;A new design of MRPC to reduce noise and crosstalk，2014 JINST 9 C07007</p>\n <p>　　8)Zhu Weiping, Wang Yi, et al. &nbsp;A thin float glass MRPC for the outer region of CBM-TOF wall. Nucl. Instr. Methos A735(2014) 277-282</p>\n <p>　　9) Zhu Weiping, Wang Yi, et al. A real-size MRPC developed for CBM-TOF. Science China, Technological Sciences, 2013, 56(11) 2821-2826</p>\n <p>　　10) Wang Jingbo, Wang Yi, et al. A realistic design of the CBM-TOF wall based modules commissioned in-beam. JINST, 2012 7 P10004</p>\n <p>　　11) Wang Yi, Fan Xingming, et al. A MRPC prototype for SOLID-TOF in Jlab. 2013_JINST_8_P03003</p>\n <p>　　12) Wang Yi, Chen Huangshan, et al. Progress of R&amp;D and production of timing RPCs in Tsinghua University. Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics research. A661, 2012: S134-S136</p>\n <p>　　13) Wang Yi, Cheng Jianping, et al. Development and evaluation of four-channel digital flash x-ray imaging system. Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics research A , v496, 2003:496-503</p>\n <p>　　14) Wang Yi, Wang Jingjin,et al. Monte Carlo simulation of image properties of an x-ray intensifying screen. Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics research A , v448, n3, 2000: 567-570</p>\n <p>　　15) Wang Yi, Wang Jingjin, et al. Portable pulsed electronic digital x-ray imager. NDT&amp;E International, V32, n4, 1999:215-218</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content xs-job tli-content-\">\n <p>● 2013.7-至今 国际RPC委员会 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;IAC委员</p>\n <p>● 2014.1-至今 期刊：Journal of Instrumentation，IOP Science RPC2014专刊主编</p>\n <p>● 2014.4-至今 &nbsp;LHC-CMS国际合作组 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;组员</p>\n <p>● 2009.1-至今 ILC CALICE合作组 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Steering board member</p>\n <p>● 2002.5-至今 美国RHIC－STAR国际合作组　　　　　　组员</p>\n <p>● 2008.10-至今 德国FAIR－CBM国际合作组　　　　　　组员</p>\n <p>● 2009.9-至今 美国Jlab-Hall A国际合作组　　　　　　　组员</p>\n <p>● 2010.6-至今 俄罗斯NICA－MPD国际合作组　　　　　 组员</p>\n <p>● 2012.8-至今 俄罗斯NICA固定靶实验国际合作组　　　 &nbsp;组员</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content reward tli-content-\">\n <p>● 获得部级科技进步二等奖1项，排名第一。</p>\n</div>\n</div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n    \n    <script>\n    $(function() {